Commentary Text: Umran Malik to Suryakumar Yadav, no run, clonked him bangggggggg on the helmet! He's done that to Maxwell the other night and now it's Suryakumar Yadav. Banged in short well outside off, SKY tries to pull it away really fine and ended up getting a thick inside edge that deflected bam onto the side of the helmet. The helmet is being changed as SKY looks a little relieved. Takes his own sweet time to reset evetything and we are good to go again....
